            "q_1": "Safety",
            "a_1": "BPA and phthalate-free, Non toxic and contains no microplastics\nCertified safe: EN14372 and to FDA standards",
            "q_2": "Care",
            "a_2": "Made from premium, long lasting materials. Dishwasher safe. Materials not suitable for use in microwave, oven, grill or steriliser.",
            "q_3": "Sustainability",
            "a_3": "All doddl products are engineered from long lasting, high-quality materials, meaning they can be used for years. However, when you have finished benefitting from your doddl, you can now rehome them (currently UK only) helping to ensure no doddl product is wasted. To rehome your doddl email Team@doddl.com and one of our team will be happy to help.",
